text: Alfonso González (born 3 October 1945) is a Panamanian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle middleweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Panama Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
